name: Design your gemstone like a jeweler (Community)
description:
Want to design your gemstone like a jeweler?


I'm delighted to share that I created this free Figma breakdown that will help you create your first gem.


But there’s more. I’ve joined the file with a combination of 3D shapes to assist you in selecting the best shape for your artwork.


Feel free to experiment with the file. Make sure to share your work and tag me in it so I can repost it.
